**[Local Training](/platform/train/cloud-training#remote-training)**|  Train locally, stream metrics to the platform| Existing hardware, privacy  
**[Colab Training](/platform/train/cloud-training#remote-training)**|  Use Google Colab with platform integration| Free GPU access  
  
